  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will examine whether the investigational drug EPO906, given by intravenous
      infusion (IV directly into the vein), is effective in shrinking tumors and preventing the
      growth of cells that cause kidney cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
